computed.name: page1
computed.formula:
return (this.firstName != "" || 
this.ci != "" ||
this.ext != "" || 
this.tipo != "" || 
this.sexo != "" ||
this.nacionalidad != "" || 
this.paisResidencia != "" || 
this.paisNacimiento != "" || 
this.calle != "" || 
this.numero != "" || 
this.departamento != "" || 
this.provincia != "" || 
this.distrito != "" || 
this.celular != "" )?"C":"";

computed.name: menuCurrent
computed.formula: return (this.page1 == "C" && this.page2 == "" && this.page3 == "")?1:(this.page1 == "C" && this.page2 == "C" && this.page3 == "")?2:(this.page1 == "C" && this.page2 == "C" && this.page3 == "C")?3:"";

computed.name: page2
computed.formula:
return (this.empresa != "" ||
this.calleEmpresa != "" ||
this.numeroEmpresa != "" ||
this.departamentoEmpresa != "" ||
this.provinciaEmpresa != "" ||
this.distritoEmpresa != "" ||
this.celularEmpresa != "" ||
this.cargo != "" ||
this.tiempo != "" ||
this.ingresoMonto != ""
)?"C":"";
